attributes.title: Armando Moves to Austin, TX: The Ostrich Farm
attributes.caption: Armando is moving down to Texas for something BIG! Along the way he and his friends from Gallos Unidos (Hector Gonzales & Santiago Ruiz) set out to film promos, enjoy the open road, and find out "what's bigger than a rooster"? In episode 1, they stop at The Rooster Cogburn Ostrich Farm in Arizona to try to find out.

attributes.title: Armando Moves To Austin, TX: The Finale
attributes.caption: Armando is moving down to Texas for something BIG! Along the way he and his friends from Gallos Unidos (Hector Gonzales & Santiago Ruiz) set out to film promos, enjoy the open road, and find out "What's bigger than a rooster"? In the finale, Armando reveals the truth of his hero's journey and grapples with leaving home, the cost of travel, growth, change and delivering a satisfying conclusion. Ya know, the simple stuff.
